A Spoiler Warning…

I’ve kept from reblogging Game of Thrones stuff because I didn’t want to spoil the first episode for any of my followers who haven’t seen it.

But with the next episode approaching and my Fandom fire burning, I can hold back no longer. Just wanted to give you a heads up that THERE WILL BE SPOILERS IN MY BLOG, RIGHT UNTIL THE NEXT EPISODE.

For all of you who don’t wish to see them, I will tag everything I post or reblog with #gotspoilers2019 so you can filter it out.

If anything goes wrong, let me know. I love you all and wouldn’t want to spoil the GoT experience for anyone. 💕💕💕

body:
Game of Thrones OC: Arlenna Baratheon (Lannister)

Basics
Name: Arlenna Jaeda Baratheon (Lannister)
Age:17 (When the story starts)
Birth date: 282 AC
Height: 5'4’’
Weight/Body Type: Slim
Skin Color: Pale
Eye Color: Blue
Hair Color: Blonde
Sexuality: Pansexual

Relationships
Parent(s): Cersei Lannister (Mother), Jaime Lannister (Biological Father), Robert Baratheon (Father)
Siblings: Joffrey Baratheon (Twin Brother), Myrcella Baratheon (Younger sister), Tommen Baratheon (younger brother), Unnamed Baratheon (half brother)
Grandparents: Tywin Lannister (Grandfather), Joanna Lannister (Grandmother)
Children: None Yet
Love Interest: Sandor Clegane (The Hound), Sansa Stark

Personality
Likes:Learning, Painting, Singing, Astrology, Wine, gambling
Dislikes: Politics, Joffrey, bugs, the dark
Habits (smoking, drinking etc.): Drinking, gambling
Hobbies:Singing, Drawing, gambling, reading, dancing
Favorite Sayings:  “Ours is the Fury”,  “Hear Me Roar!”, “A Lannister Always Pays their Debts”
Style (Elegant, shabby etc.): Elegant
Best quality: Compassion
Greatest flaw: Short Tempered                                          Worst Quality: Short Tempered                                      Traits (Kind,Sarcastic,etc.): Caring, creative, witty        Backstory: Arlenna is the twin sister of Joffrey. She is 10 minutes younger than Joffrey. She grew up her Mother’s Favorite. She noticed her Uncle Jaime was also very protective of her. She always assumed it was because they were family. Joffrey and Arlenna are very different from each other so they never really got along. Her ‘father’ Robert also got along because they both drank and gambled. Her mother Cersei hated that. Arlenna is close to Sansa and becomes very protective of her, developing a crush. On Joffrey’s name day she made him mad and pronounced that she shall marry the hound much to their Mother’s begs to Joffrey.

title: Canetas do Game of Thrones feitas em prata e ouro 18K
body:
Canetas do Game of Thrones feitas em prata e ouro 18K

As canetas do Game of Thrones são o novo (e limitado) lançamento da empresa italiana Montegrappa, que lançou a coleção com o nome de “Winter is Here”.

Cada uma delas vem com uma verdadeira obra de arte esculpida em volta, “envolvida por um estudo magistral da antiga arte da fundição por cera perdida”.

O Rei da Noite e um White Walker estão gravados na caneta com cristais de apatita…

summary: So if all the White Walkers are destroyed and they take forever North Winter with them? Does that mean it will be like The Lion,...
body:
So if all the White Walkers are destroyed and they take forever North Winter with them?

Does that mean it will be like The Lion, The Witch, and The Wardrobe. Where they start to break the White Witch’s spell and the persistent winter starts to fade into spring. Something similar?

So does that mean the lands where it’s always winter up North, that once the White Walkers are gone, it will bring the other seasons back as well?
